      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee uppureja tam\nKUNGA M tai Deena no ta\nLaupijuma/ ko tee bij atweddnu-\nfchi / ſeptinsints Wehrichus un\nſeptin tuhkſtochas Awis."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee padarrtja Derri-\nbu/ ka teem bij to KUNGU fa-\nwo Tehwo Deewu mekleht no\nwiſfas ſawas Sirds/ un no wiſ-\nfas ſawas Dwehteles."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſtam/ kaſ to KUN-\nGU Israëta Deewu ne buhtu\nmeklejs/ tam bij nokantam tapt/\ntik labbi maſam ka leelam / tik\nlabbi Wihrain ka Seewat."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee ſwehreja tam KUN-\nGAM ar ſtipru Balsi un Ga-\nwileſchann / ir ar Trummetehin\nun Baſunehin."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſfa Juhda preezn-\njahs pahr ſcho Swehreſchanu/\njo tee bij no wiſfas Sirds ſweh-\nrejſchi/ un mekleja to no wiſfa\nPrahta / un wiſch tapve no\nteem atrasts / un tas KUNGŚ\ndewe teem Duſſeſchanu wiſſ-\napkahrt."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſch nozehle arridſan\nMaëku ta Rehnixa Affus Mah-\nti/ ka ta var Rehnixinni ne buh-\ntu/ tapehz ka ta weenn negantu\nElka-Deewu bij darrifji weená\nMeschá/ un Affus iſdeldeja ar-\nridſan wiſnas Elka-Deewu/ un\nfadansija to / un fadedsinaja to\npee tahs Uppes Riḣdran."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee Augſtumi ne tap-\npe nopohſtiti no Israëta/ tomehr"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch neſſe Deen\nNammiá wiſfas eefwehtitas Le-\ntas ſawa Tehwa/ un ko wiſ-\npats bij fwehtijs / Sudrabu u\nSeltu un Trankus."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne kahds Karſch bijo-\nlihſtam trihs deſmits un pee-\ntam Gaddani tahs Waldisch-\nnas Affus."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Affus Sirde bija ſkaidra wiſ-\nfawa Laika."
    }
  ],
